  "title": "Senior Engineer (Telecommunication & Commissioning) #JTL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Project Delivery</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the design, build, and implementation of Tier-1 turnkey projects for public sector clients.</li><li>Install, configure, test, and commission telecommunication and IT solutions, ensuring smooth transition from project handover to operations.</li><li>Perform OS hardening and security compliance (e.g., CIS benchmarks, patch management, vulnerability\nremediation).</li><li>Prepare technical documentation, implementation guides, security hardening checklists and troubleshooting procedures.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Operations & Support</strong></u></p><ul><li>Provide 24/7 technical support (on a rotational basis) for mission-critical systems, ensuring minimal downtime.</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve complex issues across systems, networks, and firewalls.</li><li>Conduct Vulnerability Assessment & Penetration Testing (VAPT) in line with security policies, ensuring vulnerabilities are remediated promptly.</li><li>Collaborate with global vendors to escalate, track, and close technical issues.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</strong><br /><strong>Topaz Liang Huimin (CEI No. R1104500), email to: topaz@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 99C4599</strong></p>",
